webpackJsonp([0xa8983d27df82],{450:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p>Parses game files, translating from lua to json, and uploads to Google sheets for derived statistic analysis. Processes base units, upgrades and doctrines to calculate effective stats for each year.</p>\n<!-- end excerpt -->\n<h2>Lua to Json parser</h2>\n<p><a href="https://github.com/ratiotile/lua2json">https://github.com/ratiotile/lua2json</a></p>\n<p>The HOI3 wiki has outdated unit data from an early patch. This project reads in the game data files to produce up-to-date unit stats for the latest version of Hearts of Iron III.</p>\n<p>Turns lua tables, which are common in config files, into json objects. Uses PEGjs parser generator.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Uses HTML5 file api to select and read game lua files.</li>\n<li>Parses the lua tables into json objects.</li>\n<li>Uploads data to google sheets.</li>\n<li>Applies tech and doctrine upgrades according to game rules.</li>\n<li>Produces new spreadsheets of unit stats for each game year.</li>\n</ol>',frontmatter:{date:"January 11, 2018",path:"/projects/hoi3stats",title:"Hearts of Iron 3 Stats"}}},pathContext:{}}}});
